summary: Use libiscsi test suite against local LIO target
description: >
  The test creates a target using targetcli and runs libiscsi
  tests with iscsi-test-cu utility.
  Bi-directional CHAP credentials needs to be specified as
  env variables, normally by a tmt plan.
test: /root/.local/bin/pytest libiscsi-local.py
tag+:
  - local
tier: 0
enabled: true
adjust+:
  enabled: false
  when: distro >= rhel-10, fedora-41
  because: Test requires package libiscsi-utils, but no one for
    rhel-10 and fedora-41 yet.
